response.original_title: Cena-Brock: Prelude to the Biggest Fight of the Summer
response.overview: An in-depth look at the intense rivalry between John Cena and Brock Lesnar as they prepare for their championship clash at SummerSlam; the two men speak about their careers, opponents and what to expect in the biggest fight of the summer.
response.title: Cena-Brock: Prelude to the Biggest Fight of the Summer
